# MemPalace MCP — optional configuration
#
# MEMPALACE_PALACE_PATH: Override the palace data directory.
#
#   Default inside container: /workspace/extra/mempalace-data/palace
#   Default on host:          <project-root>/mempalace-data/palace
#
#   The palace directory must be writable and persistent across restarts.
#   It is mounted read-write into the agent container.
#
# MEMPALACE_PALACE_PATH=/path/to/your/palace
